# **8) The Rule Matrix (Miniâ€‘Spec)**

Create a table with columns: Agreement Â§ | Provider Rule Â§ | Admin Practice | What Happened | Divergence? (Y/N) | My Action (Objection/Memo) | Exhibit #.

- Goal: Every administrative action is tied to a rule (or to the absence of one). Each Y in Divergence must trigger a written action entered in My Action and an Exhibit reference. This forces disciplined, written responses and autoâ€‘builds your courtâ€‘ready archive.

